<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3442424>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Labrys khuzestanensis n. sp. (light microscopy, female). A: Pharyngeal region; B: Reproductive system; C: Part of neck; D: Anterior region; E: Amphidial opening; F: Cuticular annuli at mid-body; G: Distal part of tail showing its tip; H: Excretory pore; I: Vulva region. All scale bars =10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3442424/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3442428>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Bayesian 50% majority rule consensus tree inferred using SSU rDNA of Labrys khuzestanensis n. sp. under the GTR+G+I model. Bayesian posterior probabilities and maximum likelihood bootstrap values are given for appropriate clades in the shape BPP/ML BS. The newly obtained sequence is in bold font." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3442428/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

